--- SCENARIO: secret draft tracks pick progress in the status and reveals at the end ---
# Pick pools still go out as DMs. Per-pick progress is shown silently in the status message (k/N in)
# instead of a "@x has made their pick" line. Only two milestones ping the group: draft started and
# all picks in — each a reply that backlinks to the status message, which holds the final reveal.

--- CHAT ---
alice: /lobby
bob: /register

--- DM (alice) ---
alice: /leaders                  # alice (host is also a player) opens a private chat → DM-reachable
ambotorix: <button "{leader}">
--- DM (bob) ---
bob: /leaders                    # bob opens a private chat → DM-reachable
ambotorix: <button "{leader}">

--- CHAT ---
alice: /setDraft secret
ambotorix: <status *Status: waiting*Draft: secret*>
alice: /start
ambotorix: 🎮 Draft started by @alice* <backlink>
ambotorix: <status *Status: drafting*Picks: 0/2 in*>
ambotorix:                       # group stream so far is just the start milestone

--- DM (alice) ---
ambotorix: <image> <button "Pick *" x6 distinct>   # alice's secret pick pool
alice: <press_button "Pick *">
ambotorix: You picked {leader}*

--- CHAT ---
ambotorix: <status *Picks: 1/2 in*>                 # progress edited in silently — no group line
ambotorix:

--- DM (bob) ---
ambotorix: <image> <button "Pick *" x6 distinct>
bob: <press_button "Pick *">
ambotorix: You picked {leader}*

--- CHAT ---
ambotorix: 🎉 All picks are in!* <backlink>          # the second (and last) milestone
ambotorix: <status *Status: done*Picks:*@alice → {leader}*@bob → {leader}*>
ambotorix:                       # group stream held exactly the two milestones
